txt.en: 'Elite warriors of Khirgi still threaten our posts along the bridges dividing Fushaum. They are strong, but not invincible to fighters like yourself. We must kill these enemies who threaten our goals!'
'All gone you say?! Well done, you crafty [placeholder].'
A guard spotted you sneaking around!
Khirgi's loyal can be found in Fushaum Bal North.\n\nYou should defeat Khirgi's loyal while avoiding the guards.
Mâlatuk can be found at Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should talk to Mâlatuk.
<rgb=#FF0000>Don't let the Fushaum Guards spot you</rgb>
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
